column1: #Text=Stay Puft Marshmallow Man , through Geektropolis website .
#Text=Adrianna Prosser , host of Toronto geek culture community website Geektropolis , spent part of the convention Fan Expo Canada 2017 as the Stay Puft Marshmallow Man .
#Text=She told Wikinews that " geeking in Toronto is always such a joy , what with amazing cosplay and passionate fandoms coming together at Fan Expo !
